[{"Code":"en","Title":"Create a conversion","Slug":"documentation-template-10","ContentType":2,"Content":"<h2 data-block-id=\"mc4w387z-j4j1te-290\">Get started</h2><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">Converting between currency balances with your Xendit Global Account involves two steps:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-zr2dfz-295\" start=\"1\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-7pb6qp-296\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-h9pvjd-292\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-6\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Fund your balance</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-odt6st-297\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-vhhwej-293\"><mark data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"efdb077f-3a37-47c0-a90e-55ed55ae1a79\" data-resolved=\"true\">Create a conversion</mark></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Converting between currencies</h2><p data-block-id=\"mc4w612c-mfyv9g-402\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background:transparent;font-family:Roboto;font-size:10pt;font-weight:300;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" type=\"spanMark\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:419px;height:308px;\" type=\"spanNode\"><img data-block-id=\"mc4w43ef-qmyizj-303\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfxLIZOE0q3cPCYHvuOjB_ZXF6yz9-mBsMMbM-nGu5e_A0L1VdMU4PFZv2jHPDDxei_DQA8QGYrXdkvuzgdvZMsjCJE91F12TJZ1HP3uDD0dbgsxkwd77O8L8iFaq3N3hfj3JqnMg?key=-sCRALoqPGXPKm_M4fvtqw\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"419\" height=\"308\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4w413m-skgw69-301\">To convert between currencies directly from the Dashboard:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wf1754-374\" start=\"1\" style=\"\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-aoxsbw-375\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-18o7pg-361\">Navigate to your Home Page, or your individual Balance page.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-7okgzn-376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-qule9q-362\">Click <strong>Convert</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wzy7df-377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-lm7ws6-363\">Choose the source and destination currency balances for conversion. Your destination currency must be one of your open currency balances.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-k0mr16-378\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-vk0wbc-364\">Enter the amount you want to convert.</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4rv7-iudhas-388\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-atanh5-379\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-yii4b8-365\">You may specify either the source amount or the destination amount. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-qs26w4-380\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-nrd3uw-366\">You’ll be quoted a rate for that currency pair, as well as the amount you’ll receive. The rate refreshes after 30 seconds.</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-j93qmi-381\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-emjli8-367\">Click <strong>Save &amp; Next</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-uqihlu-382\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dl8sgt-368\">Review your Conversion details. Then click <strong>Convert</strong>. </p><blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-axnui3-413\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9hyt-1a8nl0-416\">Exchange rate may update automatically</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-zhx4bj-414\">The exchange rate may have been updated automatically with the latest rate after 30 seconds. By clicking Convert, you are accepting the updated rate. </p></blockquote></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-dmh6hu-384\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bzacuo-370\">Enter your PIN to confirm the conversion. If you’ve not created a PIN before, you’ll be prompted to create a new PIN at this stage. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9incxf-385\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bxmg0d-371\">You’ll immediately receive the converted amount in your destination currency balance upon completion of the flow. Xendit charges no fees for conversion and uses market competitive FX rates.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9lpo0o-386\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dv1bxm-372\">You may track your conversions in the <strong>Transactions</strong> page. You may also download our <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/reports-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">reports</a> to reconcile your conversions. </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4yh0jv-2nla3g-924\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Create a conversion","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Buat konversi","Slug":"documentation-template-10","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h2 data-block-id=\"mc4w387z-j4j1te-290\">Mulai</h2><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">Mengonversi saldo antar mata uang dengan akun regional Xendit Anda melibatkan dua langkah:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-zr2dfz-295\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-7pb6qp-296\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-h9pvjd-292\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-6\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Fund your balance</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-odt6st-297\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-vhhwej-293\"><mark data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"efdb077f-3a37-47c0-a90e-55ed55ae1a79\" data-resolved=\"true\">Buat konversi</mark></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Mengonversi antar mata uang</h2><p data-block-id=\"mc4w612c-mfyv9g-402\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background:transparent;font-family:Roboto;font-size:10pt;font-weight:300;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" type=\"spanMark\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:419px;height:308px;\" type=\"spanNode\"><img data-block-id=\"mc4w43ef-qmyizj-303\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfxLIZOE0q3cPCYHvuOjB_ZXF6yz9-mBsMMbM-nGu5e_A0L1VdMU4PFZv2jHPDDxei_DQA8QGYrXdkvuzgdvZMsjCJE91F12TJZ1HP3uDD0dbgsxkwd77O8L8iFaq3N3hfj3JqnMg?key=-sCRALoqPGXPKm_M4fvtqw\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"419\" height=\"308\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4w413m-skgw69-301\">Untuk mengonversi antar mata uang langsung dari Dashboard:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wf1754-374\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-aoxsbw-375\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-18o7pg-361\">Buka Halaman Beranda Anda, atau halaman Saldo individual Anda.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-7okgzn-376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-qule9q-362\">Klik <strong>Convert</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wzy7df-377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-lm7ws6-363\">Pilih saldo mata uang sumber dan tujuan untuk konversi. Mata uang tujuan Anda harus salah satu dari saldo mata uang Anda yang terbuka.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-k0mr16-378\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-vk0wbc-364\">Masukkan jumlah yang ingin Anda konversi.</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4rv7-iudhas-388\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-atanh5-379\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-yii4b8-365\">Anda dapat menentukan jumlah sumber atau jumlah tujuan. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-qs26w4-380\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-nrd3uw-366\">Anda akan diberikan kurs untuk pasangan mata uang tersebut, serta jumlah yang akan Anda terima. Kurs diperbarui setelah 30 detik.</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-j93qmi-381\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-emjli8-367\">Klik <strong>Save &amp; Next</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-uqihlu-382\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dl8sgt-368\">Tinjau detail Konversi Anda. Lalu klik <strong>Convert</strong>. </p><blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-axnui3-413\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9hyt-1a8nl0-416\">Kurs dapat diperbarui secara otomatis</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-zhx4bj-414\">Kurs mungkin telah diperbarui secara otomatis dengan kurs terbaru setelah 30 detik. Dengan mengklik Convert, Anda menerima kurs yang telah diperbarui. </p></blockquote></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-dmh6hu-384\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bzacuo-370\">Masukkan PIN Anda untuk mengonfirmasi konversi. Jika Anda belum pernah membuat PIN sebelumnya, Anda akan diminta untuk membuat PIN baru pada tahap ini. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9incxf-385\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bxmg0d-371\">Anda akan segera menerima jumlah yang dikonversi dalam saldo mata uang tujuan Anda setelah alur selesai. Xendit tidak membebankan biaya untuk konversi dan menggunakan kurs FX yang kompetitif di pasar.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9lpo0o-386\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dv1bxm-372\">Anda dapat melacak konversi Anda di halaman <strong>Transactions</strong>. Anda juga dapat mengunduh <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/reports-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">reports</a> kami untuk merekonsiliasi konversi Anda. </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4yh0jv-2nla3g-924\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Buat konversi","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"สร้าง Conversion","Slug":"documentation-template-10","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h2 data-block-id=\"mc4w387z-j4j1te-290\">เริ่มต้นใช้งาน</h2><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">การแปลงระหว่างยอดคงเหลือสกุลเงิน (currency balances) ด้วยบัญชีภูมิภาค (Global Account) ของ Xendit มีสองขั้นตอน:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-zr2dfz-295\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-7pb6qp-296\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-h9pvjd-292\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-6\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">เติมเงินเข้ายอดคงเหลือของคุณ</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-odt6st-297\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-vhhwej-293\"><mark data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"efdb077f-3a37-47c0-a90e-55ed55ae1a79\" data-resolved=\"true\">สร้างการแปลงสกุลเงิน</mark></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">การแปลงระหว่างสกุลเงิน</h2><p data-block-id=\"mc4w612c-mfyv9g-402\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background:transparent;font-family:Roboto;font-size:10pt;font-weight:300;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" type=\"spanMark\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:419px;height:308px;\" type=\"spanNode\"><img data-block-id=\"mc4w43ef-qmyizj-303\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfxLIZOE0q3cPCYHvuOjB_ZXF6yz9-mBsMMbM-nGu5e_A0L1VdMU4PFZv2jHPDDxei_DQA8QGYrXdkvuzgdvZMsjCJE91F12TJZ1HP3uDD0dbgsxkwd77O8L8iFaq3N3hfj3JqnMg?key=-sCRALoqPGXPKm_M4fvtqw\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"419\" height=\"308\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4w413m-skgw69-301\">หากต้องการแปลงระหว่างสกุลเงินโดยตรงจาก Dashboard:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wf1754-374\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-aoxsbw-375\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-18o7pg-361\">ไปที่หน้าแรก (Home Page) หรือหน้ายอดคงเหลือ (Balance page) ของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-7okgzn-376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-qule9q-362\">คลิก <strong>Convert</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wzy7df-377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-lm7ws6-363\">เลือกยอดคงเหลือสกุลเงินต้นทาง (source) และปลายทาง (destination) สำหรับการแปลง สกุลเงินปลายทางของคุณจะต้องเป็นหนึ่งในยอดคงเหลือสกุลเงินที่คุณเปิดใช้งานอยู่</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-k0mr16-378\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-vk0wbc-364\">ป้อนจำนวนเงินที่คุณต้องการแปลง</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4rv7-iudhas-388\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-atanh5-379\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-yii4b8-365\">คุณสามารถระบุได้ทั้งจำนวนเงินต้นทางหรือจำนวนเงินปลายทาง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-qs26w4-380\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-nrd3uw-366\">คุณจะได้รับอัตราแลกเปลี่ยนสำหรับคู่สกุลเงินนั้น รวมถึงจำนวนเงินที่คุณจะได้รับ อัตราแลกเปลี่ยนจะรีเฟรชหลังจาก 30 วินาที</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-j93qmi-381\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-emjli8-367\">คลิก <strong>Save &amp; Next</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-uqihlu-382\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dl8sgt-368\">ตรวจสอบรายละเอียดการแปลงสกุลเงินของคุณ จากนั้นคลิก <strong>Convert</strong></p><blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-axnui3-413\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9hyt-1a8nl0-416\">อัตราแลกเปลี่ยนอาจอัปเดตโดยอัตโนมัติ</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-zhx4bj-414\">อัตราแลกเปลี่ยนอาจได้รับการอัปเดตโดยอัตโนมัติด้วยอัตราล่าสุดหลังจาก 30 วินาที การคลิก Convert ถือว่าคุณยอมรับอัตราที่อัปเดตแล้ว</p></blockquote></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-dmh6hu-384\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bzacuo-370\">ป้อน PIN ของคุณเพื่อยืนยันการแปลงสกุลเงิน หากคุณยังไม่เคยสร้าง PIN มาก่อน ระบบจะแจ้งให้คุณสร้าง PIN ใหม่ในขั้นตอนนี้</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9incxf-385\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bxmg0d-371\">คุณจะได้รับจำนวนเงินที่แปลงแล้วในยอดคงเหลือสกุลเงินปลายทางทันทีเมื่อดำเนินการเสร็จสิ้น Xendit ไม่คิดค่าธรรมเนียมสำหรับการแปลงสกุลเงิน และใช้อัตรา FX rates ที่แข่งขันได้ในตลาด</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9lpo0o-386\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dv1bxm-372\">คุณสามารถติดตามการแปลงสกุลเงินของคุณได้ในหน้า <strong>Transactions</strong> คุณยังสามารถดาวน์โหลด <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/reports-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">reports</a> ของเราเพื่อกระทบยอดการแปลงสกุลเงินของคุณได้</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4yh0jv-2nla3g-924\"></p>","SeoTitle":"สร้าง Conversion","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Crear una conversión","Slug":"documentation-template-10","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><h2 data-block-id=\"mc4w387z-j4j1te-290\">Primeros pasos</h2><p data-block-id=\"39394a2f-a7d8-44d0-961f-3e60f5266be1\">Convertir entre saldos de Moneda con su cuenta regional Xendit implica dos pasos:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-zr2dfz-295\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-7pb6qp-296\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-h9pvjd-292\"><a href=\"/docs/documentation-template-6\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">Financiar su Saldo</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w3lqe-odt6st-297\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w3f3d-vhhwej-293\"><mark data-type=\"comment\" data-comment-id=\"efdb077f-3a37-47c0-a90e-55ed55ae1a79\" data-resolved=\"true\">Crear una conversión</mark></p></li></ol><h2 data-block-id=\"30dcfd5a-9ca8-4806-80a0-1ed43417c570\">Conversión entre Monedas</h2><p data-block-id=\"mc4w612c-mfyv9g-402\"><span style=\"color:rgb(0, 0, 0);background:transparent;font-family:Roboto;font-size:10pt;font-weight:300;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;\" type=\"spanMark\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:419px;height:308px;\" type=\"spanNode\"><img data-block-id=\"mc4w43ef-qmyizj-303\" src=\"https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfxLIZOE0q3cPCYHvuOjB_ZXF6yz9-mBsMMbM-nGu5e_A0L1VdMU4PFZv2jHPDDxei_DQA8QGYrXdkvuzgdvZMsjCJE91F12TJZ1HP3uDD0dbgsxkwd77O8L8iFaq3N3hfj3JqnMg?key=-sCRALoqPGXPKm_M4fvtqw\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"419\" height=\"308\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px;\"></span></span></p><p data-block-id=\"mc4w413m-skgw69-301\">Para convertir entre Monedas directamente desde el Dashboard:</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wf1754-374\" start=\"1\" style><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-aoxsbw-375\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-18o7pg-361\">Navegue a su Página de inicio o a su página individual de Saldo.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-7okgzn-376\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-qule9q-362\">Haga clic en <strong>Convertir</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-wzy7df-377\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-lm7ws6-363\">Elija los saldos de Moneda de origen y de destino para la conversión. Su Moneda de destino debe ser uno de sus saldos de Moneda abiertos.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-k0mr16-378\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-vk0wbc-364\">Ingrese el Monto que desea convertir.</p><ol data-block-id=\"mc4w4rv7-iudhas-388\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-atanh5-379\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-yii4b8-365\">Puede especificar el Monto de origen o el Monto de destino. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-qs26w4-380\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-nrd3uw-366\">Se le cotizará una tasa de cambio para ese par de Monedas, así como el Monto que recibirá. La tasa se actualiza después de 30 segundos.</p></li></ol></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-j93qmi-381\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-emjli8-367\">Haga clic en <strong>Guardar y Siguiente</strong>.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-uqihlu-382\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dl8sgt-368\">Revise los detalles de su Conversión. Luego haga clic en <strong>Convertir</strong>. </p><blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-axnui3-413\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9hyt-1a8nl0-416\">La tasa de cambio puede actualizarse automáticamente</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mc4w9a8r-zhx4bj-414\">La tasa de cambio puede haberse actualizado automáticamente con la tasa más reciente después de 30 segundos. Al hacer clic en Convertir, usted está aceptando la tasa actualizada. </p></blockquote></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-dmh6hu-384\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bzacuo-370\">Ingrese su PIN para confirmar la conversión. Si no ha creado un PIN antes, se le pedirá que cree un nuevo PIN en esta etapa. </p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9incxf-385\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-bxmg0d-371\">Recibirá inmediatamente el Monto convertido en su Saldo de Moneda de destino al completar el flujo. Xendit no cobra Tarifas por la conversión y utiliza tasas de FX competitivas en el mercado.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mc4w4hqy-9lpo0o-386\"><p data-block-id=\"mc4w4aym-dv1bxm-372\">Puede rastrear sus conversiones en la página de **Transacciones**. También puede descargar nuestros <a href=\"https://xendit-docs.document360.io/docs/reports-overview\" target=\"_self\" translate=\"no\">reportes</a> para conciliar sus conversiones. </p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mc4yh0jv-2nla3g-924\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Crear una conversión","Description":null}]